quran[190]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Boikarabello ba batho bo se bo le haufi haholo le bona, le hoja ba furalla ka ho hloka kutloisiso"
  21,2,"Ha ho fihla ho bona molaetsa o mocha o tsoang ho Mong`a bona, ha bao mamele bao nka e le papali"
  21,3,"Lipelo tsa bona li tletsoe ke bosaoana. Ba ipuoa lekunutung baetsalibe ba re: “Ana ha se motho ea joaloka lona? Na le ka hoheloa ke boloi le ntse le bo bona?”"
  21,4,"E re: “Mong`a ka U tseba lintho tsohle tse buoang leholimong esita le lefats’eng. U Utloa Tsohle, U Tseba Tsohle.”"
  21,5,"Ba re: “Che, tsena ke motsoebere oa litoro; kapa e be u iqapetse tsona; kapa e be ke seroki. Ha a ke a re tlele le sesupo se ts’oanang le sa baporofeta ba khale-khale, ba kileng ba romelloa ka lits’upiso.”"
  21,6,"Ho ne ho se Sechaba se neng se lumela har’a tseo Re ileng Ra li ripitla pele ho bona, le hoja Re ‘nile Ra ba romella lits’upiso: na e be ba sa tla ke kholoe"
  21,7,"Pele ho lona ha Re’a ka ra romella ho hong, e le baromuoa ba Rona kantle le batho bao Re ileng Ra ba neha ts’usumetso. A ke le botseng balateli ba Lengolo"
  21,8,"Ha Re’a ba neha ‘mele e ke keng ea ja lijo, kapa hona ho se ang’oe ke lefu"
  21,9,"Re ile Ra phethahatsa ts’episo ea Rona holim’a bona. Re ile Ra pholosa bao Re neng Re khahloa ke bona, eaba Re ripitla ba neng ba tlotse melao"
  21,10,Re le senoletse Lengolo leo e leng sehopotso ho lona. Na ha le utloisisi
  21,11,"Hana ke lichaba tse ngata hakakang tseo re ileng ra lie ripitla ka lebaka la ho tlaloa ke bosaoana, eaba Re tsosa lichaba tse ling kamor’a tsona"
  21,12,"Ha ba se ba lokela ho latsoa kahlolo ea Rona, ba qalella ho e baleha"
  21,13,"“Se baleheng, empa boelang monyakeng oo le o filoeng le malapeng a lona, hore le tle le botsoe lipotso"
  21,14,"Ba re: “Bomalimabe bo ho rona! Ruri re bile baetsalibe.”"
  21,15,"Sello seo sa bona ha se’a ka sa khaotsa, ho fihlela Re ba bokelletse joaloka koro ha e hetsoe, bafetoha lesupi"
  21,16,Ha re’a hlola leholimo le lefats’e le tsohle tse lipakeng tsa tsona ho ba papali
  21,17,"Hoja e bile thato ea Rona ea ho fumana monyaka, Re ka be Re ile Ra iketsetsa ona ho ka bo Rona, – hoja Re ne Re ratile joalo"
  21,18,"Che Re tjekeletsa leshano ka ‘Nete, leshano le hloka mokoka hoo le timelang. Ruri le tla ba mahlomoleng ka seo le se manamisang Allah"
  21,19,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng ke tsa Hae. Le manyeloi a haufi le bo teng ba Hae, Ha A ikakase hoo A ke keng a mo sebeletsa, kapa hona ho khathala ts’ebeletsong ea Hae"
  21,20,Ba Mo rorisa bosiu le mots’eare; ha ba khathale
  21,21,Kapa ebe ba ikhethetse melimo lefats’eng e ka tsosang bafu
  21,22,"Hoja e be e bile teng molimo o mong ntle ho Allah, Ruri maholimo le lefats’e a ka be a hloka taolo. Lithoriso li be ho Allah, Eena Mong`a Terone ho tsohle tseo ba Mo kopanyang le tsona"
  21,23,"A ke ke A botsoa lipotso holim’a lintho tseo A li hlolang, empa ke bona ba tla botsoa"
  21,24,"Kapa e be ba ikhethela ba bang ho ba etsa molimo ntle ho Allah? E re: “Hlahisang sesupo sa lona sa bopaki ba bo-molimo ba bona. Sena ke sehopotso sa banang le ‘na le bohle ba bileng teng pele ho ‘na, empa bongata ba bona ha ba na tsebo ea ‘nete, kahoo ba khelohile"
  21,25,"Ha Re’A s’o ka Re romella moromuoa Re sa ka Ra mo neha ts’usumetso,: “Ha ho na molimo o mong kantle ho ‘Na, Allah, kahoo khumamelang le ho sebeletsa ‘Na.”"
  21,26,"Ba re: “Ea Khaphatsehang Lereko, Allah, o na le mora. Lithoriso li be ho Eena! Ke makhabunyane a hlomphehang"
  21,27,"Ha ba buee ho fihlela Eena A fana ka puo, e bile ba etsa ts’ebetso ho latela taelo ea Hae"
  21,28,"O tseba tsohle tse ka pel’a bona le tse kamor’a bona, ba ke ke ba buella mong le mong kantle le ho bao Allah a khahlisoang ke bona, ba bile ba thothomela ke ts’abo malebana le Eena"
  21,29,"Ha e mong oa bona a ka re: “Ruri! Ke ‘na `Mopi kathoko ho Allah”, eo eena Re tla mo putsa ka Lihele. E leng kamoo Re putsang baetsa-libe kateng"
  21,30,"Na e be mahana-tumelo ha ba tsebe hore maholimo le lefats’e e ne e le karolo e le ‘ngoe, eaba Re ea li arola; le hore Re ile Ra etsa lihloliloeng tsohle tse phelang ka metsi? Na e be ba sa tla ke ba kholoe"
  21,31,"Re behile Lithaba tse tsepameng holim’a lefats’e hore le se reketle ka bona, e bile re entse litsela tse pharalleteseng, e le hore ba tle ba iphumanele tataiso"
  21,32,Re entse leholimo marulelo a sireletsehileng. Le hoja ba furalla lits’upiso tsa lona leholimo
  21,33,"Ke Allah Ea hlotseng bosiu le mots’ehare, le lona letsatsi le ‘ngoeli. E ‘ngoe le e ‘ngoe ea tsona e tsamaea mocheng oa eona"
  21,34,"Ha Re’a s’o ka Re fana ka bophelo bosafeleng ho motho ofe kapa ofe pele ho uena. Eng! Haeba u ka shoa, na e be ba ka phela kahosafeleng"
  21,35,"Moea ka mong o tla latsoa lefu, Re le lekile ka botle le bobe. Bohle le tla boela ho Rona"
  21,36,"Nakong eo mahana-tumelo a u lemohang, ba u nka u le sesomo, ba re: “Ana ke eloa ea phoqang melingoana ea lona?” Ba bile banyefola lipuo tsohle tsa ea Tletseng Lereko"
  21,37,"Motho o hlotsoe a le lehala: Haufinyane Ke tla le bonts’a lits’upiso tsa Ka, ka nako eo le ke ke la nkopa ho li potlakisa"
  21,38,"Ba re: “Ke neng ts’episo eo e tlang ho phethahatsoa, haeba u hlile u buoa ‘nete?”"
  21,39,"Hoja e be mahana-tumelo ba ne ba mpa ba tsebile ka nako ea mohla ba tlang ho sitoa ho phutla mollo o tla beng o le mahlong a bona le ka mor’a bona, ba ke keng ba thusoa"
  21,40,"Che, nako eo e tla ba oela ka ts’ohanyetso, hore e tle e ba ts’erehanye hoo ba tlang ho sitoa le ho e thibela, kapa hona ho fumants’oa nyehlisetso"
  21,41,"Ba ‘nile ba so’ngoa Baromuoa pele ho uena, empa lits’omo tseo tsa bona li baetselitse lesakana-la-nkope bao bohle ba neng ba ba phoqa"
  21,42,"E re: “Ke mang ea le lebetseng bosiu le mots’eare malebana le khalefo ea Allah, ea Tletseng Lereko.” Empa ba furalla polelo ea Mong`a bona"
  21,43,"Kapa e be bana le melingoana e ka ba pholosang khahlanong le Rona? Ruri! ba ke keng ba ithusa ka bo-bona, leha e le hona ho its’ireletsa khahlanong le Rona"
  21,44,"Che Re fane ho bona le ho bo-ntata bona ka lintho tse hloekileng tsa bophelo ba lefats’e, ho fihlela bophelo bo lelefetse malebana le bona. Ha ba bone kamoo Re chakelang naha kateng, le hona ho e khutsufatsa ka hanyane meeling e ka mathoko? Na e be ke bona ba tla hlola"
  21,45,"E re: “Ke mpa feela ke le hlaha leseling ka ts’usumetso.” Empa haele litholo ha li utloe pitso nakong eo li eletsoang"
  21,46,"Haeba moea oa kahlolo ea Mong`a hau o ne o ka ba ama, Ruri ba ne ba tla re: “Tahlehelo ke’a rona! Hobane re bile baetsa- libe.”"
  21,47,"Re tla hlopha lipekho tsa Toka tsa Letsatsi la Kahlolo, e le hore ho se be moea o ka qhekelloang ka letho. Le hoja o tla be o lekana le qoba ea koro ka boima, empa re tla o tlisa boikarabellong. Re lekane ts’ebetso ea ho ka hlahloba"
  21,48,"Re ile Ra neha Moshe le Aarone ts’iea ea kahlolo ea botle le bobe, Leseli le Molaetsa le sehopotso sebakeng sa ba etsang botle"
  21,49,"Ba ts’abang Mong`a bona lekunutung, le ho ba hlokolosi ka hora ea kahlolo"
  21,50,"Sena ke Molaetsa o halalelang oo Re o senotseng: na le ona le tla o latola"
  21,51,"Re ile Ra neha Abrahama kholo e nepahetseng khale, Re bile hlokolosi ka eena"
  21,52,"Hopola mohla a reng ho ntata’e le ho batho ba habo: “Ke ling lits’oants’o tsena tseo le li rapelang?”"
  21,53,"Ba re: “Re fumane bo-ntata rona ba li khumamela.”"
  21,54,"Abrahama a re: “Ruri lona le bo-ntata lona le bile phosong e hlakileng.”"
  21,55,"Ba re: “Joale, uena u re tliselitse ‘nete, kapa u e mong oa ba soasoang?”"
  21,56,"Abrahama a re: “Che, Mong`a lona ke Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e, Ea A hlotseng; le ‘na ke paki ea seo"
  21,57,"Ka Allah, ke na le leano ka melingoana ena ea lona, hoba le tsamae, le furalle"
  21,58,"Eaba o e khaola likotoana kaofela, a siea se seholo har’a tsona, hore ba tle ba se botse lipotso"
  21,59,"Ba re: “Ke mang ea thuileng melingoana ea rona tje? Ruri! E tlameha e le e mong oa baetsa-libe.”"
  21,60,"Ba re: “Re utloile mohlankana a buoa ka eona: ea bitsoang Abrahama.”"
  21,61,"Ba re: “mo tliseng ponts’eng ea batho, hore ba tle ba fane ka bopaki.”"
  21,62,"Ba re: “Abrahama! Na ke uena ea entseng melingoana ea rona ka tsela e tje?”"
  21,63,"Abrahama a re: “Che se entsoe-, ke ena e kholo. Li botseng haeba li tseba ho bua.”"
  21,64,"Ba qamaka koana le koana, ba re: “Ruri ke rona ba phoso.”"
  21,65,"Ba hlajoa ke lihlong, ba re: “Ruri! U tseba hantle hore lits’oants’so tsena ha li tsebe ho buoa.”"
  21,66,"Abrahama a re: “Joale le khumamela lintho tse ke keng tsa le thusa ka letho, leha e le hona ho le hlahisetsa kotsi kathoko ho Allah"
  21,67,“Masoabi a be ho lona le lintho tsohle tseo le li rapelang ntle ho Allah! Ha le na kelello na?”
  21,68,"Ba re: “Mo cheseng, le sireletse melingoana ea lona haeba le ka khona.”"
  21,69,"Re Re: “Mollo! Bata, o be sets’abelo ho Abrahama!”"
  21,70,"Eaba ba etsa sefi khahlanong le eena: empa Ra ba etsa ba lahlehetsoeng ka ho fetisisa"
  21,71,"Re ile Ra mo pholosa le Lota, Ra ba lebisa naheng eo Re e hlonolofalitseng molemong oa lichaba tsohle"
  21,72,"Ra mo sitsa ka Isaaka, le Jakobo e le mpho ea tlatsetso. Ra ba apesa ka toka e mong le e mong oa bona"
  21,73,"Ra ba etsa Baetapele ba tataisang ka Taelo ea Rona, Ra ba susumelitsa ho etsa liketso tse lokileng, le ho phethahatsa lithapelo tsa mehla le ho fana ka linyehelo; ba re sebeletsa kamehla"
  21,74,"Lota le eena Re ile Ra mo neha Kahlolo le Tsebo, Ra mo pholosa har›a motse o neng o etsa manyala. Ruri! E ne e le batho ba oetseng sebeng le bona bojela-thoko"
  21,75,Ra mo atametsa haufi le Mohau oa Rona. Hobane e ne e le e mong oa ba lokileng
  21,76,"Hopola Nooe ha ne a memetsa pele ho koano: Ra mamela thapelo ea hae; Ra mo pholosa le ba ntlo ea hae mesarelong e ts’abehang"
  21,77,"Ra mo thusa khahlanong le batho ba latotseng lits’enolo tsa Rona: Ruri! E ne e le batho ba oetseng sebeng: Re ile Ra metsa kaofela ha bona metsing"
  21,78,"Hopola Davida le Salomone, mohla ba neng ba fana ka kahlolo malebana le linku tsa batho tse neng li tlole bosiu eaba li kena ts’imong bosiu; Re bile lipaki kahlolong ea bona"
  21,79,Re ts’ollela Salomone kutloisiso ea taba eo; ho e mong le e mong oa bona Re fane ka Kahlolo le Tsebo. Ebile ka matla a Rona ho etsa hore maralla le linonyana li bine lithoriso tsa Allah hauts’oane le Davida. Ebile Rona Baetsi ba lintho tseo
  21,80,"Ke Rona ba mo rutileng mahlale a ho etsa liaparo tsa ts’epe molemong oa lona, ho le ts’ireletsa lintoeng tsa lona. Ana ha le na teboho"
  21,81,"E bile ka matla a Rona ho Salomone mabapi le moea o neng o foka ka matla hore o khutse. Tlas’a taelo ea hae, ‘nga ea naha eo Re e hlohonolofalitseng. Hobane Re hlokolosi holim’a lintho tsohle"
  21,82,"Re ile Ra mo neha matla holim’a karolo e ‘ngoe ea bo-liabolosi ba neng bapharumela likhetla sebakeng sa hae, ba bile ba etsa mosebetsi o mong, e bile Rona ba neng ba ba lebetse"
  21,83,"Hopola Jobo ha a memetsa ho Mong`a hae, a re: “Ruri! Mats’oenyeho a nkaparetse, ke Uena Ea Khaphatsehang Mohau ho feta bohle ba bonts’ang Mohau.”"
  21,84,"Eaba Re mamela thapelo ea hae: Ra phumula mats’oenyeho ao a neng a mo aparetse, le hona ho mo neha lelapa la hae, Ra le menahanya ha beli, – e le Mohau o tsoang naleng ea Rona le eona khopolo ho ba sebeletsi ba Rona"
  21,85,"Hopola Ishmaele, Idris le Zu’l-kifl. Kaofela ba ne ba ena le mamello le tsitlalello"
  21,86,Re ile Ra ba amohela Mohaung oa Rona. Hobane ba ne ba le har’a ba lokileng
  21,87,"Hopola Zu’n-nun, mohla a neng a tsamaea ke khalefo, a hopola hore ha Re na matla holim’a hae, empa u ne a memetse har’a lefifi, a re: “Ha ho `Mopi e mong ntle ho Uena Allah. Tlotla e be ho Uena! Ruri! Ke bile moetsa-libe.”"
  21,88,"Eaba Re mamela thapelo ea hae, Ra mo pholosa mathateng ao. Ke kamoo Re pholosang ba kholoang kateng"
  21,89,"Hopola Zakaria mohla a neng a memetsa ho Mong`a hae: “Mong`a ka! U se ntlohelle ke sena ngoana, le ha ele Uena mojalefa ea Molemo"
  21,90,"Re ile Ra mo mamela, Ra mo sitsa ka Johanne, eaba Re neha mosali oa hae matla a ho mo tsoalla ngoana. Ba ne ba potlakela tlholisanong ea mesebetsi e metle: ba memetsa ho Rona ka lerato le ka tlhompho, ba ikokobetsa ho Rona"
  21,91,"Le ea neng a hloka sekoli, Re ne Re bolulele moea oa Rona ka ho eena, eaba Re ba etsa sesupo eena le mora oa hae ho merabe eohle"
  21,92,"Ruri! Tumelo ena ea lona, ke tumelo e le ‘ngoe; ‘Na ke Mong`a lona, kahoo le nthapele ke inot`si"
  21,93,"Empa matlobo a morao-rao, a khaotse tumelo ea bona likotoana har’a bona, le hoja kaofela ha bona ba tla boela rona"
  21,94,"Athe mong le mong ea etsang toka, e bile e le molumeli, ts’ebetso ea hae ha e ke ke ea latoloa. Re tla e boloka molemong oa hae"
  21,95,"Ho behiloe thibelo holim’a sechaba sefe kapa sefe seo re ileng ra se ripitla: hore ba ke ke ba khutla"
  21,96,"Ho fihlela batho ba Gog le Magog ba lokolotsoe, ba phasaphasa ho hloella lithaba tsohle"
  21,97,"Ke moo, Ts’episo ea ‘Nete e tla beng e atametse; mahlo a mahana-tumelo a tla be a le nchocho ke le ts’oalo! batla re: “Ruri re malimabe! Re phetse tlas’a bolebalibasena. Che, re bile baetsa-libe"
  21,98,"Ruri! Lona le melingoanaeo le e khumamelang ntle ho Allah, le libeso tsa Lihele. Le tla tla ho tsona"
  21,99,"Hoja e be lintho tseo e ne e le Allah, li ne li ke ke tsa atamela moo, empa kaofela li tla phela kamoo"
  21,100,"Sa bona kamoo ke seboko, ha ho seo ba tla se utloa"
  21,101,"Bao Re ba sitsitseng pele ka mosa oa Rona, ba tla ba hole-hole le teng"
  21,102,"Ba ke ke ba utloa le haele molumo o monyenyane oa teng, ba tla nyakalla ka har’a seo lipelo tsa bona li se labalabelang"
  21,103,"Ba ke ke ba nyaroha ke letsoalo le thothometsang, etsoe manyeloi a tla ba amohela ka hore: “Lena ke Letsatsi – leo esaleng le le ts’episoa"
  21,104,"Ke mohla Re tla phutha maholimo joaloka ha mongoli a phutha buka e ngotsoeng. Joaloka ha Re ile Ra simolla tlholeho sethathong, Ruri Re tla e pheta hape. Seo ke ts’episo e tlamang ho Rona. Ruri! Re tla e phethahatsa"
  21,105,"Pele ho mona Re ngotse Lipesalemeng, kamor’a Lengolo la Moshe hore: “Makhabunyane a ka a tla ja lefats’e lefa.”"
  21,106,Ruri! Ho teng molaetsa o totobetseng ho batho ba khumamelang Allah ka tieo
  21,107,Re u romeletse o se letho ntle le mohau libupuoeng tsohle
  21,108,"E re: “Seo ke se senoletsoeng ke hore `Mopi oa lona ke `Mopi A le mong. Na joale le inehela ho eena?”"
  21,109,"Empa ha ba furalla, E re: “Ke le feteselisitse molaetsa ka mokhoa o ts’oanang le ka ‘nete ho lona kaofela, ha ke na tsebo ea hore na seo le se ts’episitsoeng se hole kapa se haufi ho le hokae"
  21,110,“Ke Eena ea tsebang tsohle tseo le li buoang pepeneneng le tseo le li patang
  21,111,"“Ha ke na tsebo hore na ke teko ho lona, kapa mpho ea nakoana ea bophelo.”"
  21,112,"E re: “Oho Mong`a ka! A k’u ahlole ka ‘nete.” “Mong`a rona Ea Khaphatsehang Lereko, Eo Thuso Ea Hae e ts’oanelang ho kopuoa khahlanong le seo le se manehang ho Eena. Ka lebitso la Allah, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"
  22,1,"Oho lona batho! T`sabang Mong`a lona. Hobane Ruri haele ho reketla mohla Hora ea kahlolo, e tla ba ntho e nyarosang"
  22,2,"Mohla letsatsi leo le tlang ho e bona, motsoetse e mong le e mong o tla lebala ho ants’a lesea la hae le eena mokhachane o tla beleha lesea le’a s’o ho be maemong; uena, ke mohla o tla bona e ka batho ba tahiloe, le hoja ba sa tahoa: khalefo ea Allah e tlabae boima"
  22,3,"Har’a batho ho teng ba ngangisanang ka Allah ka ho hloka tsebo, ba latela mahoholi afe kapa afe a liabolosi"
  22,4,"Empa ba laetsoe hore mong le mong ea tla etsa Satane motsoalle oa hae, o tla mo khelosa le ho mo tataisetsa kahlolong ea Mollo"
  22,5,"Oho lona batho! Haeba le na le khoao ka Letsatsi la Tsoho, bonang! Re le hlotse ka lerole, The’re le lehloele, eaba Re le etsa nama e nang le sebopeho, kapa e senang sona, hore Re tle Re hlakise lits’upiso tsa Rona ho lona. Re etsa hore ho lule ka har’a limpa seo Re se ratang ho fihlela nako ea pallo ea sona, e be kamor’a moo Re le hlahisa le le masea, ebe Re le neha kholo, hore le tle le fihlele lilemo tse lokelang. Har’a lona ho teng ba shoang ba sa le banyane, ho teng ba fihlelang lilemo tsa botsofali, hore ba tle ba se ke ba tseba letho kamor’a ho ba ba be le tsebo. U bona lefats’e le se nang bophelo le hlobotseng, empa ha Re romella pula ho lona, le khutlela bophelong le hona ho ts’akhunya liliba le ho hlahisa limela ka bobeli tse khahlang"
  22,6,"Sena ke hobane Allah ke Eena ‘Nete: ke Eena ea fanang ka bophelo ho ba shoeleng, U na le Matla holima tsohle"
  22,7,Hobane Ruri hora e ea tla eo ho seng khoao ka eona; Allah U tla tsosa bohle mabitleng
  22,8,"Empa har’a batho ho na le ba ngangisanang ka Allah ka ho hloka tsebo, kapa tataiso esita le lona Lengolo le fanang ka Leseli"
  22,9,"O furalla ka boikakaso o khelosa batho ka thetso tseleng ea Allah. Masoabi a tla mo aparela bophelong bona, mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo Re tla etsa hore a latsoe Kahlolo ea Mollo"
  22,10,"Ho tla thoe: “Sena ke moputso oa seo matsoho a hau a ileng a se romella nale, Ruri Allah ha se mohatelli oa makhabunyane a hae.”"
  22,11,"Ho teng har’a batho b`a sebeletsang Allah ka monahano o fokolang hoo eka reng haba oeloa ke lehlohonolo, ebe ba khotsofetse, empa haeba bomalimabe bo ka ba oela, ba phakisa ba nyebella. Joale, e be bophelo ba lefats’e lena bo ea ba phonyoha esita le Bo-tlang. Seo ke tahlehelo e pepenene"
  22,12,"Ba memetsa ho melingoana e ke keng ea ba hlahisetsa kotsi le e nyenyane, le hona ho ba putsa ka letho. Seo ke ho khelohela hole-hole kannete"
  22,13,Ba memetsa ho eo mathata a hae a leng haufi haholo ho feta moputso; Ruri setsoalle se joalo ke se fosahetseng le eena mothusi eo ke’a bolileng
  22,14,Ruri! Allah U tla amohella ba kholoang ba sebetsang ka toka ka har’a Lirapa tse linoka li phallang. Hobane Allah U phethisa seo a se rerang
  22,15,"Ebang ho na le mong le mong ea nang le monahano o fosahetseng oa hore Allah a ke ke a fana ka tlholo ho eena lefats’eng lena le ho bo-tlang, ha a ke a leketlise thapo marulelong a ntlo ea hae, e be o’a iphanyeha. Joale, a tle a bone hore na malepa a hae a tla ke a suthise seo se mo halefisisang"
  22,16,"Ke kamoo Re senolang Lits’enolo tse hlakileng, Ruri Allah U tataisa ea ikhethetseng Eena"
  22,17,"Bohle ba kholoang ts’enolong ena, ba latelang Bo-juda, Ma- Sabian, Ba-Keresete ng, le Baloing esitana le Bahedeneng, – Ruri! Ke Allah ea tla ahlola lipakeng tsa bona mohla letsatsi la tsoho. Ruri ke Allah U tla ahlola lipakeng tsa bona ka Letsatsi la Kahlolo. Hobane Allah ke paki holima lintho tsohle"
  22,18,"Na ha le’a s’o bone hore lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng li rapela Allah, letsatsi, ngoeli, linaleli, lithaba, lifate, le linonyana le batho bohle, le hoja ho na le ba ba ngata bao kahlolo eba tobileng. Bao Allah a ba apesitseng sekhobo, ha ho ope ea ka ba nehang tlhompho. Hobane! Ruri Allah U etsa seo A se ratang"
  22,19,"Mahlakore ana a mabeli, a hohlana ka bobeli khahlanong le Mong`a bona: Ba latolang,-ba tla etsetsoa liaparo tsa mollo; ba tla ts’eloa lihloohong ka metsi a belang"
  22,20,Lintho tsohle tse ka har’a limpa tsa bona li tlang ho qhibilia `moho le letlalo la bona
  22,21,Ho bile ho teng Meutloa ea ts’epe sebakeng sa bona
  22,22,"Ka linako tsohle batla lakatsa ho tsoa kamoo ka maqakabetsing, empa ba tla qobelloa ho boela kateng, ho tla thoe: “Latsoang kahlolo ea Mollo.”"
  22,23,"Allah U tla amohela bohle ba kholoang ba etsa liketso tse lokileng ho kena ka har’a lirapa tse linoka li phallang, ba tla apesoa lipetja tsa khauta le tsa masapo, Liaparo tsa bona e tla ba tsa silika"
  22,24,Hobane ba ile ba tataisoa ka molaetsa o machosi; ba tataiselitsoe tseleng ea Ea Ts’oanetsoeng ke Tlotla
  22,25,"Haele ba latotseng, ba sitisa batho ho kena tseleng e lebisang ho Allah le ‘nqalong e Halalelang ea thapelo, eo Re e khethetseng batho bohle hoba ‘moho ho eona; baahi ba moo le baeti, ka bobeli ba na le tokelo ea moo; mong le mong ea ikemiselitseng ho baka pherekano moo, Ruri re tla mo latsoisa kahlolo e mahlonoko"
  22,26,"Bonang Re nehile Abrahama ‘nqalo ea ntlo e halalelang, (Re Re): “Ho se be letho leo o ka le kopanyang le ‘Na, u be u hloekise Ntlo ea Ka malebana le batla e pota-pota le hona ho ema haufi le eona `moho le ba tla khumama ba ithapalatse"
  22,27,"“U phatlalatse bosepheleli ho batho bohle: ba tla tla ho uena ba tsamaea ka maoto, ha ba bang ba tla tla ba kaletse likamele; ba tla tla ba hlaha ka likhoro tsohle"
  22,28,"Ho tla paka lintho tse nang le molemo ho bona, le ho keteKa lebitso la Allah ka Matsatsi a fanoeng holim’a makhomo ao A ba sitsitseng ka ona sebakeng sa lihlabelo. Joale, jang le be le fane ka eona ho mafutsana"
  22,29,"Ba tlohele ho qetela lits’ebeletso tse ngolileong malebana le bona, le hona ho rapela le ho potoloha Ntlo e Halalelang ea Mathomo.”"
  22,30,"Mong le mong ea hlomphang litokelo tsa bohlokoa tsa Allah, seo se molemo ho eena kapel’a Mong`a hae. Makhomo a molemo ho lona ele lijo nakong ea bosepheleli kantle le seo le kileng la se joetsoa. Kahoo, qobang lits’ila tsa bahedene le mashano"
  22,31,"Le be le ‘nete tumelong ea Allah, le se mo kopanye le batlatsetsi; hobane ea kopanyang Allah le batlatsetsi, o ts’oana leha e ka o ile a theoha marung, eaba o hlothoa ke linonyana, kapa a fefoloa ke moea ho mo lahlela sebakeng se hole-hole"
  22,32,"Seo: Mong le mong ea ikitlaetsang ho hlompha lits’upiso tsa Allah, ka ho etsa mahlabelo a liphoofolo Ruri seo se tsoa khalalelong ea lipelo"
  22,33,Mahlabelo ao a molemo ho lona sebakeng sa pallo; mathethong sebaka sa tsona lihlabelo tseo se thoko le Ka’ba
  22,34,"Re fane ka taelo ea lihlabelo ho merabe eohle ea batho, hore ba tle ba keteke lithoriso tsa Allah holim’a makhomo ao A ba nehileng ona ele lijo; etsoe `Mopi oa lona ke `Mopi A le mong, kahoo ineheleng ho Eena. Fana ka litaba tse molemo ho ba ikokobetsang"
  22,35,"Bao lipelo tsa bona li tlaloang ke ts’abo nakong eo ho buuoang ka Allah, ba mamellang holim’a lintho tsohle tse ba hlahelang ka ts’ohanyetso, le ho phethahatsa lithapelo esita le ho nyehela ka tseo Re ba sitsitseng ka tsona"
  22,36,"Likamele tsa sehlabelo Re li etselitse hoba har’a Litsu’po ho tsoa ho Allah. Le na le melemo e mengata ho tsona. Kahoo, le hlalose lebitso la Allah holim’a tsona nakong eo li tjammeng ka mekhahlelo. Joale, ha li se li oele fats’e kamor’a ho hlajoa, le ka itjella le hona ho fepa ba hlokang le bohle ba qelang ka hlompho. Ke kamoo Re etsang hore le be le taolo holim’a tsona kateng, hore le tle le fane ka liteboho"
  22,37,"Ha se nama, kapa mali a tsona a tla finyella ho Allah, empa ke tumelo ea lona e tla finyella ho Eena. Ke kamoo Re etsang hore le be le taolo holim’a tsona, hore le tle le tlotlise Allah, A tle A le tataise. Fana ka litaba tse molemo tsena ho ba etsang tse lokileng"
  22,38,"Ruri! Allah U ts’ireletsa bohle ba kholoang. Allah ha A rate ea furallang tumelo, a hloka le teboho"
  22,39,Ntoa e lumeletsoe ba loanang hobane ba hateletsoe; Allah U Matla Oohle ho ba thusa
  22,40,"Ba phalalisitsoeng malapeng a bona hobane ba itse: “Mong`a rona ke Allah,” na ha se Allah ea thibang lehlakore le leng la batho ka le leng, Ruri! Ho ka be ho ile ha heletsoa Litempele, Likereke, li-Sinakhokhe le li-Mosque moo lebitso la Allah le tlotlisoang ka mehla eohle. Allah U thusa ea mo thusang. Hobane Allah U Matla Oohle, U Ts’abehile Matleng, –"
  22,41,"Bao e reng ha Re ba neha matla lefats’eng, ebe ba phethahatsa lithapelo le hona ho fana ka linyehelo le ho khothaletsa toka, le ho felisa bobe. Ho Allah ke poloko ea litla-morao tsa litaba tsohle"
  22,42,"Ebang ba u hanyetsa, le Batho pele ho bona ba ‘nile ba etsa joalo ka Baprofeta ba bona, – batho ba habo Nooe esitana le mohlobo oa ba-Ad le ba-Thamud"
  22,43,Le ba habo Abrahama le Lota
  22,44,"Le Balekane ba batho ba Mediane. Le Moshe o ‘nile a latoloa; empa Ke ile Ka fana ka nyehlisetso ho mahan-atumelo ha nakoana, eaba Ke ba neha kotlo kamor’a moo, nyeliso ea Ka ho bona e bile e ts’abehang joang"
  22,45,"Ke Lichaba tse kae tseo Re ileng Ra li ripitla nakong eo li neng li le sebeng, hoo e ileng ha sala e le lesupi ho fihlela kajeno, ke liliba tse kae tse ileng tsa sala shalabeng esita le tsona lipaleisi"
  22,46,"Na ha ba e s’o hahlaule le lefats’e, hoo lipelo tsa bona li ka sisimohang esitana le tsona litsebe tsa bona li ka utloang? Hobane! Ruri ha se mahlo a bona a foufetseng, empa ke lipelo tse ka lifubeng tsa bona"
  22,47,"Ba u kopa ho potlakisa kahlolo, le hoja Allah A ke ke A sitoa ts’episong ea Hae, Ruri! Haele letsatsi le kapel’a Allah, le shebahala le ka balloa lilemong tse sekete ho latela palo ea lona"
  22,48,"Hana ke Lichaba tse kae tseo ke ileng ka li neha nyehlisetso, le hoja li ne li le sebeng? Hoo ke ileng ka li neha kotlo khabareng. Ruri! Poelo e ho ‘Na"
  22,49,"E re: “Oho batho! Ke rometsoe ho lona feela ho fana thlokomeliso e hlakileng"
  22,50,"Bohle ba kholoang ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, ts’oarelo e teng bakeng sa bona `moho le nala e babatsehang"
  22,51,"Empa haele ba tsitlaletseng khahlanong le lits’enolo tsa Rona, – e tla ba balekane ba Mollo.”"
  22,52,"Ha Re’a s’o ka Re romella moromuoa, kapa moporofeta pele ho uena, ebe eba Satane ha a mo hoka-hoke ka malepa. Empa Allah U hlakola sohle seo Stane a se etsang. Allah U phethahatsa lits’enolo tsa Hae. Hobane Allah U tletse tsebo, U Seli"
  22,53,"E le hore A tle A etse seo liabolosi a se etsang teko ho bao lipelo tsa bona ho tletseng maloetse, le bao lipelo tsa bona li thatafetseng, – Ruri! Baetsalibe ba karohanong e totobetseng, –"
  22,54,"Le ba nehiloeng tsebo ba tle ba tsebe hore ke ‘nete e tsoang ho Mong`a hau, ba tle ba kholoe ho eona le lipelo tsa bona li tle li inehele ka boikokobetso ho Eena. Hobane! Ruri Allah U tataisa bohle ba kholoang tseleng e totobetseng"
  22,55,"Bohle ba hanyetsang tumelo ba ke ke ba khaotsa ho ba le khoao holim’a eona, ho fihlela hora e ba oela ka ts’ohanyetso, kapa ba tloha ba oeloa ke Letsatsi la Tlokotsi"
  22,56,"Matla a Puso mohla letsatsi leo, e tla be e le a Allah feela. Ke Eena Ea tla ahlola lipakeng tsa bona. Haele ba tla beng ba kholoa, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng ba tla kena ka har’a Lirapa tsa Nyakallo"
  22,57,"Ba hanyetsang tumelo, ba latola lits’enolo tsa Rona, ho teng Kahlolo e soabisang"
  22,58,"Bohle ba phaphathehang malapeng a bona ts’ebeletsong ea Allah, ba fenethoa, kapa ba shoa, Ruri! Allah U tla ba sitsa ka nala e babatsehang. Ruri Allah Ke Eena Ea fanang ka nala"
  22,59,"Ruri! U tla ba amohela sebakeng se tla ba khahla. Hobane! Allah U Tseba Tsohle, U na le Kutloelo-Bohloko"
  22,60,"Ke kamoo ho leng kateng. Mong le mong ea iphetetsang ka bohloko bo ts’oanang le boo a ileng a bo utloisoa, e be hamorao o boetse o phetoa ka bona, Ruri! Allah U tla mo thusa. Hobane! Allah ke Eena Ea tlosang libe, o ts’oarela- joalo-joalo"
  22,61,"Ke hobane Allah U entse hore bosiu bo sehe mots’eare tsebe le mots’eare o sehe bosiu tsebe, hobane Allah U ultoa tsohle, U bona tsohle"
  22,62,"Hobane Allah – Ke ‘Nete, seo ba bitsang ho sona kantle ho Eena, ke leshano, Allah U Phahametse Tsohle, U Moholo- Holo"
  22,63,"Na ha le bone kamoo Allah A romellang pula lefats’eng kateng e tsoa marung, ebe lefats’e le apareloa ke botala ka letsatsi le hlahlamang? Ruri! Allah U Hloekile, U Hlokolosi"
  22,64,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le lefats’eng ke tsa Hae. Ruri! Allah ha A hloke letho, U ts’oanetsoe ke lithoriso tsohle"
  22,65,"Na ha le bone kamoo Allah A entseng hore lintho tsohle tse teng lefats’eng li be le molemo kateng ho lona? Likepe li sesa holim’a leoatle ka taelo ea Hae, U ts’oere leholimo hore le se ke la oela fats’e kantle le ka tumello ea Hae. Ruri! Allah U Tletse Khauhelo, U Mohau o Khaphatsehang ho batho"
  22,66,"Ke Eena ea le nehileng bophelo, ke Eena ea tla etsa hore le shoe, A boele A le nehe bophelo hape. Ruri! Motho ke sebupuoa se hlokang teboho"
  22,67,"Re fane ka lits’ebeletso tsa keteko le meetlo ho lichaba tsohle tseo ba ts’oanetseng ho li phethahatsa; ba se u ngangise ka taba eo, empa u ba biletse ho Mong`a hau. Hobane! Ruri uena u latetse Tataiso e Nepahetseng"
  22,68,"Empa ba u phehisa khang, E re: “Allah U tseba ka botlalo tsohle tseo le li etsang"
  22,69,“Allah U tla ahlola lipakeng tsa lona mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo khahlanong le seo le neng le hanyetsana ka sona
  22,70,"Na ha le tsebe hore Allah U tseba lintho tsohle tse leholimong esita le tsohle tse lefats’eng? Ruri! Seo se ngoliloe, seo se bobebe ho Allah"
  22,71,"Empa ba khumamela lintho tse sa kang tsa senoleloa matla le hanyane, kantle ho Allah, tse bileng li senang le tsebo. Baetsalibe ha ba na mothusi"
  22,72,"Ha Lits’enolo tsa Rona tse Hlakileng li phetoa, u tla bona tatolo lifahlehong tsa mahana-tumelo; ho sale hanyane ba futuhela ba ba phetelang lits’enolo tsa Rona. E re: “Na nka le bolella ka se seng se nyarosang ho feta lits’enolo seo? Ke Mollo! Oo Allah a o ts’episitseng mahana-tumelo. Phello ea leeto e babang"
  22,73,"Oho batho! Papiso ke ena, kahoo thehang tsebe: Lintho tseo le li bitsang ho tsona ntle ho Allah li sitoa ho hlola leha e le ts’ints’i, le ha li ka kopano ‘moho ka morero oo. Haeba ts’ints’i e ka nka ho hong ho tsona, li ke ke tsa e pholosa ho eona. Kahoo, ka bobeli bakopi le bakopuoang ba ea fokola"
  22,74,"Ba mpa ba entse tekanyo ka Allah: Hobane! Ruri Allah ke Ea Matla, Ea phethahatsang Thato ea Hae"
  22,75,"Allah U khetha baromuoa har’a manyeloi le har’a batho. Allah ke Eena Ea utloang tsohle, o bona tsohle"
  22,76,"U tseba tsohle tse kapel’a bona esita le tsohle tse kamora’ bona, lipotso tsohle li tla boela ho Allah"
  22,77,"Oho lona ba kholoang! Inamang, le ithapalatse le rapele Mong`a lona, le etse ka toka, hore le tle le atlehe"
  22,78,"Le be le tsitlalle tseleng ea Allah joaloka ha e le tokelo ea hae ho tsitlallela. U le khethile, ha A le belesa ka mojaro o boima tumelong; ke tumelo ea ntat’a lona Abrahama. Ke eena ea le rehileng Mamuslim linakong tsa khale-khale le ka har’a"